                                <img decoding="async" width="1616" height="1696" src="../wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Our-Software-Payment-.png" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-5988" alt="" srcset="https://zaman-it.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Our-Software-Payment-.png 1616w, https://zaman-it.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Our-Software-Payment--286x300.png 286w, https://zaman-it.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Our-Software-Payment--976x1024.png 976w, https://zaman-it.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Our-Software-Payment--768x806.png 768w, https://zaman-it.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Our-Software-Payment--1464x1536.png 1464w" sizes="(max-width: 1616px) 100vw, 1616px" />													</div>
